pageTitle: High School Sports | Sept. 9 2011 football Provo-Orem | Deseret News
textBeforeTable: Rushing Individual stats Cole Payne worked hard all night to get open, and it paid off as he caught three touchdown passes. Matt Gay also had a good night kicking for Tigers. Taylor Camp threw four TD passes for Orem, while Provo's Kyle Larsen found the end zone three times in the loss.
